      "created_at": "2013-04-01T00:52:37.000Z",
      "title": "Tell HN: Flag PR \"April fools pranks\"",
      "url": "",
      "author": "unimpressive",
      "points": 256,
      "story_text": "Fellow lusers,<p>I would like to appeal that you flag all uninspired april fools pranks until april second. \nThe truth of the matter is that april fools (Which I think some have called the \"hackers holiday\") has been ruined by oversaturation\nand PR departments. Instead of being a funny unexpected string of pranks and absurdism, the experience has become a droning hum\n of buzzing marketers and disrupted services.<p>By keeping the front page pure, it may be possible for a few <i>good</i> pranks to actually surprise and entertain.<p>Thank you.",
